Nutrient data for: CADBURY CHOCOLATE DRINK-INSTANT FUDGE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 00000096033210
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Fat-reduced cocoa powder (21%), whey powder (from MILK), skimmed MILK powder, inulin, milk chocolate (6%) [MILK, sugar, cocoa mass, cocoa butter, vegetable oils (palm and shea in various proportions), emulsifiers (E442, sunflower lecithin), flavourings], glucose syrup, palm oil, flavourings, salt, sugar, thickener (carrageenan), MILK proteins, anti-caking agent (E551), sweeteners (aspartame, acesulfame K), emulsifier (E471). Cocoa, Sugar: traded in compliance with Fairtrade Standards. Visit www.info.fairtrade.netContains a source of phenylalanine. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 11/24/2016
